      "context": "div.padding-section-large > div.w-richtext > p",
      "en": "The information contained in this communication is intended solely for the individual or entity to which it is addressed. It may contain confidential and/or legally privileged information. Any view or opinion presented is solely that of the author and does not necessarily represent that of the IOI Group of Companies. Any review, forwarding, dissemination, copying, printing or other use of, or taking any action in reliance on the contents of this information by persons or entities other than the intended recipient is strictly prohibited and may be unlawful. If you have received this communication in error, please notify us immediately by responding to this eMail and then delete it from your system. While the IOI Group of Companies attempts to sweep eMails and attachments for viruses and worms, it does not guarantee that either are virus or worm-free and that we accept no liability for any damage sustained as a result of viruses or worms.",
      "cn": "本通讯所含信息仅供其所指明之个人或实体使用，可能含有保密及/或受法律保护之资料。文中所表达之任何观点或意见仅代表作者本人，未必代表 IOI 集团下属公司之立场。除指定收件人以外的任何人或实体，不得查阅、转发、传播、复制、打印或以其他方式使用本资料，亦不得依据其内容采取任何行动；任何此类行为均属严格禁止，且可能构成违法。如您因疏失而收到本通讯，请立即回复本邮件通知我方，并将其从您的系统中删除。IOI 集团下属公司虽尝试对邮件及附件进行病毒与蠕虫扫描，但不保证其完全不含病毒或蠕虫，对因病毒或蠕虫造成之任何损害概不承担责任。"
